org.ensembl.variation.datamodel
Interface LDFeature

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable, Feature, Locatable, Persistent, java.io.Serializable
public interface LDFeature
extends Feature

A linkage disequilibrium between two VariationFeatures. The location is a single location node that covers both VariationFeatures and any intervenening gap.

Author:
Craig Melsopp
